1
00:01:09,959 --> 00:01:11,159
Why are you crying like this?

2
00:01:16,799 --> 00:01:17,680
I dreamed of

3
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,400
my great-grandmother.

4
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:22,159
She cheated with a Japanese man

5
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:23,359
and was called a traitor.

6
00:01:23,719 --> 00:01:25,400
They had a big fight

7
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,560
over the divorce paper.

8
00:01:28,359 --> 00:01:30,480
No, she would never be a traitor.

9
00:01:30,599 --> 00:01:31,319
Okay.

10
00:01:31,719 --> 00:01:32,680
I see.

11
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:33,560
I know.

12
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,760
Don't cry.

13
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:37,519
You must remember,

14
00:01:37,959 --> 00:01:38,879
you are Jiang Xun now,

15
00:01:38,879 --> 00:01:39,920
not Song Jin'an.

16
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,079
And,

17
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,480
have you ever thought

18
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,079
why you are the only one

19
00:01:46,079 --> 00:01:47,879
who has these dreams frequently?

20
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,519
Maybe these dreams

21
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:52,040
are trying to tell you something.

22
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:53,519
It's not a bad thing.

23
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:56,760
Hmm.

24
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,799
Don't cry.

25
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,800
Let's go.

26
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:10,800
Hmm.

27
00:02:17,439 --> 00:02:18,240
Alright.

28
00:02:18,719 --> 00:02:20,879
For the sake of me being your servant,

29
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,360
can you smile?

30
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:29,000
Smile.

31
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:30,560
Smile again.

32
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:34,240
That's right.

33
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,639
I want you to be happier.

34
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,759
Then I'll take what you said

35
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,479
as

36
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:47,039
your confession.

37
00:02:48,319 --> 00:02:49,360
No backing out.

38
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,800
So,

39
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:07,680
you agree?

40
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,360
Hello, mom, what's up?

41
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:05,680
About what you asked me,

42
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,599
actually, after your great-grandfather died,

43
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,080
your great-grandmother was labeled a traitor,

44
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:12,120
and gave birth to your grandpa alone in the Port City.

45
00:04:12,639 --> 00:04:14,159
The Jiang family was very concerned

46
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:14,879
about her traitor identity.

47
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,680
They also suspected

48
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,319
whether the child in her belly

49
00:04:18,319 --> 00:04:19,439
was the true blood of the Jiang family.

50
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:20,519
Mom,

51
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,759
I think there's more to this story.

52
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:24,439
We can't just speculate.

53
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,600
I've made up my mind.

54
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,040
I'm going to Hong City.

55
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:28,439
That's it.

56
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,600
Ms. Lin,

57
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:38,959
I'm sorry

58
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:40,839
for embarrassing you in front of the staff

59
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,040
in the office.

60
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:43,439
It's okay.

61
00:04:43,439 --> 00:04:45,240
Playing good cop and bad cop

62
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,560
can help them make decisions faster.

63
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,240
Is everything done?

64
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,319
The cultural relics have finished customs procedures

65
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,519
and loaded onto the special flight.

66
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,920
There are about two hours before takeoff.

67
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,360
Is there anything else I can do for you?

68
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,560
If I could count on you,

69
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:03,720
I wouldn't have to do it myself, would I?

70
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:09,360
You'd better not cause any more trouble.

71
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,560
Otherwise,

72
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,160
I can't cover for you.

73
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,199
Understand?

74
00:05:28,639 --> 00:05:29,439
Old Feng,

75
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:32,000
Ke Yu'ang and the others are about to go to the airport.

76
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,759
Have we been approved

77
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:35,680
for a second check on the artifacts?

78
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,000
Evidence was provided too late.

79
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,160
We'll have to handle this as a special case.

80
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:39,240
Wait for my message.

81
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:40,399
Don't act without permission.

82
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,959
There's no time.

83
00:05:48,759 --> 00:05:49,920
You look so worried.

84
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:53,839
Shut up.

85
00:06:04,759 --> 00:06:05,759
After returning to Hong Kong,

86
00:06:05,759 --> 00:06:07,439
some artifacts still need to be repaired.

87
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,040
Later,

88
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,360
let me introduce you to

89
00:06:10,639 --> 00:06:11,560
my junior sister.

90
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,319
Junior sister.

91
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,680
Here.

92
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,040
Let me introduce you.

93
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,000
This is my junior sister,

94
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:20,879
Jiang Xun, the conservator

95
00:06:21,079 --> 00:06:22,000
who comes to Hong Kong with the exhibition.

96
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:23,199
Xun.

97
00:06:23,199 --> 00:06:25,439
This is Mr. Lin, the supervisor

98
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:26,959
the Shan Yuan International Charity Foundation

99
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,560
sent to oversee the exhibition.

100
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,600
Hello, Jiang Xun.

101
00:06:33,199 --> 00:06:34,319
Lin Chuyi.

102
00:06:36,199 --> 00:06:38,160
You're really beautiful, Miss Jiang.

103
00:06:38,519 --> 00:06:41,040
No wonder Ke Yu'ang always gives you a pass.

104
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,199
Miss Jiang,

105
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:49,040
are you just fellow students with him?

106
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,399
You two look like a good match.

107
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,519
You're too kind, Ms Lin.

108
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,079
I have a boyfriend.

109
00:06:59,079 --> 00:07:00,120
Miss Jiang,

110
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,920
my mistake.

111
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,759
I heard

112
00:07:03,759 --> 00:07:05,519
you joined the outreach

113
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:06,959
temporarily for personal reasons.

114
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:08,040
Since you joined,

115
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,959
we've had all sorts of strange incidents.

116
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,480
No matter how excellent,

117
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,839
you need to be vetted thoroughly.

118
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,959
We can't ruin our reputation

119
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:17,800
at home and abroad.

120
00:07:18,519 --> 00:07:19,959
Mr. Lin, you came to Rongzhou in person,

121
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,519
so you must have investigated everything.

122
00:07:22,519 --> 00:07:25,279
The accidents you mentioned have nothing to do with me.

123
00:07:25,959 --> 00:07:27,360
That's just how I am.

124
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:31,040
I always speak frankly and keep things professional.

125
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,600
With a capable assistant like you,

126
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:36,360
your company should make a golden statue of you.

127
00:07:41,759 --> 00:07:42,800
It's still early.

128
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:44,120
Would you like to sit for a while?

129
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:06,839
Master.

130
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,040
The list for the Hong Kong trip has changed.

131
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:11,959
Mrs. Lu's name is added,

132
00:08:11,959 --> 00:08:13,079
but someone is missing.

133
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:15,439
Master,

134
00:08:15,639 --> 00:08:16,639
Mrs. Lu is going to Hong Kong,

135
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:17,399
and you didn't know it?

136
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:18,639
Cut the crap. Who's missing?

137
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,759
Ke Yu'ang's assistant.

138
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,919
Feifei, open this.

139
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:37,000
Captain Feng, the file is approved.

140
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:40,960
Okay, I see.

141
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,159
Hello.

142
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,919
Start the action.

143
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,320
What's up, Master?

144
00:08:49,559 --> 00:08:50,720
Is there a problem?

145
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,440
Well,

146
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,639
I'll stay here

147
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,200
to communicate with the airport department.

148
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,639
You notify Feng

149
00:08:57,639 --> 00:08:58,440
to quickly

150
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,519
track down the whereabouts of Ke Yu'ang's assistant.

151
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:00,639
Okay.

152
00:09:13,799 --> 00:09:15,799
It's almost time, let's board.

153
00:09:19,039 --> 00:09:20,159
[Attention, passengers,]

154
00:09:20,159 --> 00:09:21,919
[this is a special flight to Hong Kong City.]

155
00:09:22,159 --> 00:09:24,600
[Due to a recent international money laundering case]

156
00:09:24,799 --> 00:09:25,799
[involving artifacts,]

157
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,320
[we need your cooperation.]

158
00:09:28,639 --> 00:09:30,519
[We will be conducting a second security check]

159
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:31,720
[on your carry-on luggage.]

160
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,039
[Thank you for your cooperation.]

161
00:09:33,399 --> 00:09:34,679
Haven't we already passed security?

162
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:35,480
Why do we need to be checked again?

163
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:35,960
Yeah.

164
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:37,799
As Chinese citizens,

165
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,960
it's our duty to cooperate with the investigation.

166
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,519
I'm willing to accept the investigation.

167
00:09:42,559 --> 00:09:43,360
Thank you.

168
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,279
Sir.

169
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,960
Operation cancelled.

170
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,720
I can't.

171
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,279
It's meaningless now.

172
00:10:24,879 --> 00:10:25,879
Cancel it.

173
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:36,360
Oh, no. Why did I miss so many calls?

174
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:50,480
Is that Shen Shutu?

175
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:52,559
Why is he here?

176
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:57,960
200,000 yuan.

177
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:25,320
Master,

178
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,440
we got the recent call records

179
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,679
of Ke's assistant.

180
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,440
One of them

181
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,600
is the number of a boat owner.

182
00:11:31,919 --> 00:11:33,360
He wanted to leave Rongzhou by boat.

183
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,279
Yes, he might be trying to escape by sea.

184
00:11:35,879 --> 00:11:37,679
I'm on my way to Rongxi Pier.

185
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:40,480
It seems Ke Yu'ang is using a feint.

186
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,120
Don't act rashly.

187
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,919
Follow Captain Feng's orders.

188
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:45,279
I'll be there soon.

189
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:46,240
Don't worry, master.

190
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:19,080
According to Article 24 of the Counter-Espionage Law

191
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,759
of the People's Republic of China,

192
00:12:20,759 --> 00:12:22,759
when national security personnel

193
00:12:22,759 --> 00:12:25,320
carry out counter-espionage tasks,

194
00:12:25,759 --> 00:12:28,120
they shall show their work permit as prescribed,

195
00:12:28,159 --> 00:12:30,080
and have the right to check the identity of Chinese citizens

196
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:32,080
or foreigners,

197
00:12:32,279 --> 00:12:35,919
and inquire relevant individuals and organizations.

198
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,039
For those whose identity is unclear

199
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:39,200
and are suspected of espionage,

200
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:41,559
they can check their belongings.

201
00:12:41,879 --> 00:12:43,519
When we encounter national security personnel

202
00:12:43,519 --> 00:12:45,080
performing their duties according to law,

203
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,639
we should actively assist

204
00:12:46,639 --> 00:12:48,639
and cooperate with the national security agency.
